Set Up Permissions and Licenses
Administrators can grant permissions to certain groups of people, allowing them the access they need. For example, a fulfillment operator has to see how an order progresses, but doesn’t need access to admin tools.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.
